	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok...here's the way I see it. Do you like to play with other people? Sure people like having a Magician around **cough** for their pets and their ability to summon food/water. It take a bit more thought to play a Wizard. You have to think about how much damage has been do so that you don't get aggro'd or EVAC at later level. Until your mid 20's though the mage will be easier to play, but I feel that it is more challenging (therefore more fun) to play a Wizard. HAPPY HUNTING<br>&nbsp;<br>Just cause I'm a Monk doesn't mean I can pull =P</td></tr>
