	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>just one thing Id like to add here<br><br>Wizards do not get pets.<br>They get a spell at level 60 called Flaming Sword of Zuxl, or something like that<br><br>This requires a target to cast, and summons a VERY low level 'flaming sword' to attack your target. it hits for about 50 points a pop, and if it gets hit once its dead. It will continue to damage you oponent until it gets hit or the mob dies, at which point it disapears. It does not follow orders or follow you around waiting to be aggroed, it will not taunt a mob off of you, or switch from the mob you cast it on to another mob thas beating your brains out. All it is, is a way for wizards to do melee damage without worrying about skills or getting within range.<br>this is basicly a spell reserved for Dragon and God type encounters or other similar mobs with hitpoints in the tens of thousands, as the mana cost for summoning this thing is also astronomical, And its only good for one mob at a time.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
